  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the effects of early administration of probiotics on acceleration of enteral
      feeding, and on growth of very low birth weight infants, newborn infants with birth weight
      less than 1500g are administered Bifidobacterium bifidum twice a day.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
